<A>__{enter a hallway just in time to see two claridge's employees reach down and haul away the unconscious body. our heroes have missed the fight but shep and bill are delighted anyway. bill brushes his hands (one of his favorite gestures) with satisfaction, as if he had thrown the punches himself:}
