<D>__{her name is nikki. she holds men's teeth. she sits at the bar and she drinks champagne.}
<C>__{bill}
<P>__{(significantly)}
<D>__{boys, she's gonna be a lot of trouble.}
<A>__{drinks are served. a moment of silence as they imbibe. nikki's hand shakes as she lifts her glass, spilling some champagne. she laughs, embarrassed.}
