<A>__{around her neck, on a slender chain, nikki carries a small lorgnette. it opens with a spring and has small rectangular lenses. she uses it frequently, peering at unfamiliar objects in her helpless, nearsighted way. on shep's remark, she whips it out to stare at him, mildly offended. he raises his drink to his lips and turns to her, speaking out of the side of his mouth:}
<C>__{shep}
<P>__{(off frink)}
<D>__{pay no attention. sometimes he goes away.}
